    dc:title "Review of the family Anthogonidae (Diplopoda, Chordeumatida), with descriptions of three new species from the Balkan Peninsula" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.240309> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.240309>
    dc:description "FIGURES 85 – 88. Balkan anthogonids in their natural habitats. 85: Egonpretneria sp., female from the Ponor na Štirovači Cave, Velebit Mt. (photo by A. Kirin); 86: Macrochaetosoma troglomontanum Absolon & Lang, 1933, male from the Kuna Špilja Cave, Biokovo (photo by R. Ozimec); 87: Haasia likana (Strasser, 1966), female from the Manita Peć Cave, Velebit Mt. (photo by T. Dražina); 88: Haasia stenopodium (Strasser, 1966), female from the Lukina Jama Pit, Velebit Mt. (photo by M. Pavlek). Without scale. Size of specimens and ratios between sizes of specimens are not real." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/240309/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

